_:N355aa486d62949c7ace38893ad8f02fb <http://schema.org/text> "We're committed to promoting equality, fairness and respect. Our customers can expect to be treated in a manner that promotes understanding, dignity and respect." .
_:N355aa486d62949c7ace38893ad8f02fb <http://schema.org/image> <https://www.gov.uk/assets/frontend/govuk_publishing_components/govuk-schema-placeholder-4x3-194fde4197f00e669f6f52c182df2ed707bfb2024c9ef39f7a2ed20da62b90eb.png> .
_:N355aa486d62949c7ace38893ad8f02fb <http://schema.org/headLine> "Equality and diversity" .
_:N216ddfd1a3074922946c7f0a096f64be <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://schema.org/Organization> .
_:N216ddfd1a3074922946c7f0a096f64be <http://schema.org/url> <https://www.gov.uk> .
